  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.4,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "- Hi, district leaders."
      },
      {
        "start": 1.7,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "I'm Victoria from Khan Academy."
      },
      {
        "start": 4.1,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "We're excited to share with\nyou some groundbreaking work"
      },
      {
        "start": 6.5,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "that we're doing when it\ncomes to student assessments."
      },
      {
        "start": 9.0,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "We know districts are\nswamped with solutions"
      },
      {
        "start": 11.7,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "that provide endless data,"
      },
      {
        "start": 13.9,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "but fail to deliver\nreal, actionable insights"
      },
      {
        "start": 17.5,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "that lead to greater student achievement."
      },
      {
        "start": 19.6,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "As we reimagine the\nKhan Academy experience"
      },
      {
        "start": 22.4,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "for teaching and learning,"
      },
      {
        "start": 24.7,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "we are now also introducing\ninterim assessments."
      },
      {
        "start": 27.8,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "Assessments that not\nonly measure progress,"
      },
      {
        "start": 30.3,
        "duration": 4.6,
        "text": "but give instructional leaders\nand teachers data, insights,"
      },
      {
        "start": 35.0,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "and personalized student learning journeys"
      },
      {
        "start": 37.4,
        "duration": 1.7,
        "text": "to accelerate outcomes."
      },
      {
        "start": 39.1,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "I'll start by showing you\nwhat's already available,"
      },
      {
        "start": 41.6,
        "duration": 3.2,
        "text": "and then we'll look at what's\ncoming in the near future."
      },
      {
        "start": 44.8,
        "duration": 4.5,
        "text": "This all builds on our use\nof responsible, effective AI."
      },
      {
        "start": 49.3,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "As part of a 45-minute assessment,"
      },
      {
        "start": 51.6,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "students will see a range of item types,"
      },
      {
        "start": 54.2,
        "duration": 4.4,
        "text": "including a two-part explain\nyour thinking, or EYT item,"
      },
      {
        "start": 58.7,
        "duration": 3.4,
        "text": "facilitated by our new\nSocratic, conversational AI tool"
      },
      {
        "start": 62.1,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "for assessments, Khanductor."
      },
      {
        "start": 64.2,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "After students respond to a\nmore traditional item type,"
      },
      {
        "start": 67.7,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "Khanductor asks thoughtful\nfollow-up questions"
      },
      {
        "start": 70.4,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "about the test concept"
      },
      {
        "start": 72.1,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "to surface a student's deeper reasoning,"
      },
      {
        "start": 74.2,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "uncovering conceptual understandings,"
      },
      {
        "start": 76.4,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "and even unfinished learning"
      },
      {
        "start": 78.0,
        "duration": 3.8,
        "text": "that traditional right or\nwrong items can't reveal."
      },
      {
        "start": 81.8,
        "duration": 2.5,
        "text": "Also, we're really inspired seeing"
      },
      {
        "start": 84.3,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "that through the\nconversation With Khanductor,"
      },
      {
        "start": 86.7,
        "duration": 1.1,
        "text": "we're noticing that students"
      },
      {
        "start": 87.8,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "are able to show more of what they know,"
      },
      {
        "start": 90.1,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "even if they don't answer\nthe question correctly."
      },
      {
        "start": 92.3,
        "duration": 3.6,
        "text": "A lot of research has gone\ninto developing Khanductor"
      },
      {
        "start": 95.9,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "and its ability to gauge\na student's thinking."
      },
      {
